### Apply this brand to a project

```bash
/design-extractor:apply-design {{ brand.slug | default('brand-slug') }}
```

This copies the per-brand SKILL.md into your project's `.claude/skills/` so Claude auto-loads {{ brand.name | default('Brand') }}'s design rules whenever you ask for "{{ brand.name | default('Brand') }}-style" anything.

